    E Commerce FrontEnd
============================

    1 create an angular project -     **ng new roject_name**
    
    2 run angular -    **ng s -o**
    
    3 add bootstrap in index

    4 add font awsome in style.css

    5 lazy loading - its a  process of loading      components modules etc, It improves application loading time -                              **ng g m module_name --route module_name --module app.module**

    6 add <router-outlet></router-outlet> inside app.component.html

    7 create components that should lazy loaded in the product module
-all product - **ng g c products/all-product**
-cart - **ng g c products/cart**
-wishlist - **ng g c products/wishlist**

    8 setup path for each component - product.module.ts

    9 path redireccting

    10 page not found component -  **ng g c page-not-found**

    11 header and footer
    **ng g c footer**
   **ng g c header**


   12 component designing

   13 backend integration

   14 angular service  -  **ng g s products/api**

   15 import HttpClientModule in product module from **import { HttpClient } from '@angular/common/http';**

   16 dependancy injection of httpclient in constructor

   17 frontend backend connection

   18 design of wish list and cart

   19 search concept
   ng g p products/pipes/filter

   20 add to cart - BehaviorSubject